OL,3,CPoet who documented cancer struggle
OL,4,Cwins prestigious Eisteddfod chair
OL,6,FA father-of-three from Carmarthenshire
OL,7,Fhas been awarded a prestigious award
OL,8,Fat this year's National Eisteddfod in
OL,9,FWrexham after submitting a poem about
OL,10,Fbeing diagnosed with cancer.
OL,12,FTudur Hallam was presented with the
OL,13,FEisteddfod Chair after judges praised
OL,14,Fhis work which documented his
OL,15,Fdiagnosis in August 2024 and how he
OL,16,Fhas subsequently managed life with the
OL,17,Fillness.
