OL,3,CPoet who documented cancer struggle
OL,4,Cwins prestigious Eisteddfod chair
OL,6,FThis is the second time that Mr Hallam
OL,7,F- who is a retired Swansea University
OL,8,Fprofessor - has received the award
OL,9,Fafter winning at the Blaenau Gwent and
OL,10,FValleys National Eisteddfod in 2010.
OL,12,FHowever despite his win, Mr Hallam
OL,13,Fsaid that he was initially unsure
OL,14,Fwhether he would submit the poem for
OL,15,Fjudgement after finding out that
OL,16,Finitial treatment to manage the cancer
OL,17,Fhad been unsuccessful.
