OL,6,FHowever he says on reflection he now
OL,7,Fsees his work as a "celebration of
OL,8,Flife". He said: "I see this as a
OL,9,Fcelebration of life, of what you can
OL,10,Fachieve with friends, with the love of
OL,11,Fyour family."
OL,13,FMr Hallam was visibility emotional
OL,14,Fduring the awarding ceremony at the
OL,15,Fpavilion where he was officially named
OL,16,Fas this year's winner.
