OL,3,CPoet who documented cancer struggle
OL,4,Cwins prestigious Eisteddfod chair
OL,6,F"It was a wonderful experience. Of
OL,7,Fcourse it was very emotional
OL,8,Fespecially when I rose to my feet,
OL,9,Fembraced my children, but eventually I
OL,10,Fdid manage to relax and enjoy the
OL,11,Fceremony. I really did enjoy it."
OL,13,FEntrants at this year's competition
OL,14,Fwere required to submit a long poem or
OL,15,Fselection of poems under the umbrella
OL,16,Ftheme of dinas (city) .
